channel.title: Need help with Intern317 (Written from scratch)
channel.description:
Though it isn't very much. I started writing this not long ago and have ran across some problems. I was wondering if someone more experienced, and by experienced I don't mean can rename and recompile a source. If you know anything about server sockets and setting up a basic listener could you please attempt to help retarded me...
Here is the link to my source: [url=http://uppit.com/I43GW1]http://uppit.com/I43GW1[/url]
It consists of 3 classes:
[ul][li]com.intern.core.Initiate[/li] [li]com.intern.core.Server[/li] [li]com.intern.util.Output[/li][/ul]
It's a very small attempt at a client listener so will take no time to download and look through.
[b]Edit[/b]: I made this using IntelliJ IDEA so the conventions and spacing may be a little distorted in the everyday text editor.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: March 20, 2009, 11:04:17 pm[/size][hr]Hmm I'm not surprised no one from this community could help me.
